status:
This is the magic of AFM. It's always a pleasure to play with this amazing toy.
The images attached here are of the surface topographic 2D and 3D AFM images of a Blu-Ray Disc (I took the images 
). AFM, extraordinarily, can resolve the features of a surface of a material in three dimension down to atomic level. Thanks to Gerd Binnig and Heinrich Rohrer.
